{"tid":1865163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(極危急)請全連登傾力支持醫護，製造輿論","createTime":"2020-02-06T04:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T06:37:45.000Z","uid":221035,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd7d7fe9458d2db4d8226a393ef00af1486612b","tid":1865163,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"下個星期會點？<br />\n<br />\n1 醫護人員被逼無裝返工<br />\n2 有人繼續罷工<br />\n3 有人集體請病假<br />\n4 有人即時辭職<br />\n5 醫護情緒崩潰<br />\n6 香港成大型隔離營<br />\n7 開始大規模社區爆發<br />\n<br />\n到時唔係淨係林鄭背負所有污名，係所有醫護界有say既人，仲有成個醫管局都要負責<br />\n<br />\n哩個禮拜罷工，群情洶湧<br />\n但背後係咩？<br />\n上個星期開始，集體請病假<br />\n一抽到隔離病房即刻辭職呀<br />\n成個醫護系統會崩潰呀！<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家都明白，個後果俾你想像中更嚴重<br />\n唔係淨係跪唔跪或者係咪繼續罷嘅問題<br />\n係醫護系統以及醫護人員徹底崩潰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家狂spread以下文宣：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VfeYtN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VfeYtN.jpg&h=84dcc07b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2282Vq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2282Vq.jpg&h=771f65e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sTwRgfr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsTwRgfr.jpg&h=88b402f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6TWed18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6TWed18.jpg&h=11975797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n局員工陣線副主席羅卓堯：<br />\n<br />\n1⃣袁教授與其勸醫護復工，不如勸醫管局盡快與我們談判。<br />\n<br />\n2⃣未來醫護人員對醫管局無曬希望，繼續罷工，甚至集體離職，醫管局要承擔一切責任，而後果係香港共同面對。<br />\n<br />\n3⃣究竟要罷工繼續落去，定係我地可以係談判桌上滿足醫護人員切身既訴求，令佢地可以安全返回工作環境，依個就係醫管局，以至專家學者要做的抉擇。<br />\n<br />\n4⃣我相信袁國勇都好想醫護人員復工既時候都可以安全工作，如果能夠做到呢一點，我本人都願意成為dirty team 既一份子，進入隔離病房工作。"},{"pid":"abf519f8971375f00034d074b396de44d478331b","tid":1865163,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:40:08.000Z","msg":"集體離職!!"},{"pid":"3bb4bcec83e0d6bd6e792da7d523b31d7c06bded","tid":1865163,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"請原諒我係咁出post"},{"pid":"9b51b3b0cecac8cb56781250f0d08aac74508092","tid":1865163,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:40:27.000Z","msg":"輿論上唔樂觀"},{"pid":"27316cd84334d8a071ad358f30b12b4e2b70af11","tid":1865163,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:41:34.000Z","msg":"醫護人員好需要大家支持"},{"pid":"359ac7e33f6278c4131859af65fa6b515d68a534","tid":1865163,"uid":46170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:42:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5497523c0b7639238607bca360d0b4e21cfb8e9","tid":1865163,"uid":322044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聯署嗰班人去咗邊"},{"pid":"98de801ca98bfa65afe0de39b45525461fca3f8b","tid":1865163,"uid":16845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:42:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53942d5099f71ace627fe30f05f81f3eee188187","tid":1865163,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"其他工會籌備成點？<br />\n<br />\n如果醫護下個星期復工嘅話，最緊要係輿論上大家都要支持佢哋嘅決定<br />\n<br />\n不過醫護夠唔夠裝備開工又係另一件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520f5b60c6df4b5e1309bf11404fa6430974fe04","tid":1865163,"uid":76681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撐"},{"pid":"933264c87fc6170e77e9d6f8946a3f9137f3a5a1","tid":1865163,"uid":168425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1b918e3e378bbe5c26205c1c9021d5102ba0cef4","tid":1865163,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:46:20.000Z","msg":