ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T21:15:30.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"70b5df812b17b5a4fe82c651e2cefc7c77d8d5af","tid":1865163,"uid":203476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T21:15:57.000Z","msg":"tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3fb5f72385d48580755971d2d6dcb8af9d7b68c","tid":1865163,"uid":65524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T21:46:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bf5f08e91a8dbdc7d273184d61c92cd3bb1d07","tid":1865163,"uid":171938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T21:48:01.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0216f5d43342c20397529f99711b3edb7c0d2e2c","tid":1865163,"uid":156702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccd7d7fe9458d2db4d8226a393ef00af1486612b","tid":1865163,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"下個星期會點？<br />\n<br />\n1 醫護人員被逼無裝返工<br />\n2 有人繼續罷工<br />\n3 有人集體請病假<br />\n4 有人即時辭職<br />\n5 醫護情緒崩潰<br />\n6 香港成大型隔離營<br />\n7 開始大規模社區爆發<br />\n<br />\n到時唔係淨係林鄭背負所有污名，係所有醫護界有say既人，仲有成個醫管局都要負責<br />\n<br />\n哩個禮拜罷工，群情洶湧<br />\n但背後係咩？<br />\n上個星期開始，集體請病假<br />\n一抽到隔離病房即刻辭職呀<br />\n成個醫護系統會崩潰呀！<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家都明白，個後果俾你想像中更嚴重<br />\n唔係淨係跪唔跪或者係咪繼續罷嘅問題<br />\n係醫護系統以及醫護人員徹底崩潰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家狂spread以下文宣：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VfeYtN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VfeYtN.jpg&h=84dcc07b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2282Vq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2282Vq.jpg&h=771f65e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sTwRgfr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsTwRgfr.jpg&h=88b402f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6TWed18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6TWed18.jpg&h=11975797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n局員工陣線副主席羅卓堯：<br />\n<br />\n1⃣袁教授與其勸醫護復工，不如勸醫管局盡快與我們談判。<br />\n<br />\n2⃣未來醫護人員對醫管局無曬希望，繼續罷工，甚至集體離職，醫管局要承擔一切責任，而後果係香港共同面對。<br />\n<br />\n3⃣究竟要罷工繼續落去，定係我地可以係談判桌上滿足醫護人員切身既訴求，令佢地可以安全返回工作環境，依個就係醫管局，以至專家學者要做的抉擇。<br />\n<br />\n4⃣我相信袁國勇都好想醫護人員復工既時候都可以安全工作，如果能夠做到呢一點，我本人都願意成為dirty team 既一份子，進入隔離病房工作。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T21:53:03.000Z","msg":"香港人爭氣d!!"},{"pid":"9e12ddd4b51ccd2f8e4a2547f092cd71199793db","tid":1865163,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T21:54:00.000Z","msg":"香港人支持醫護<br />\n<br />\n林鄭有心玩拖字決<br />\n<br />\n醫護人員要便好心理戰<br />\n<br />\n不要怕，心情放鬆一點"},{"pid":"1c452e9b6b78ce8737a344eb11a7cbdb2d6a5225","tid":1865163,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T21:54:43.000Z","msg":"千萬不要比情緒影響到自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥一定會死拖蘭拖"},{"pid":"dc17285b06267ebb92c01ba530d0fc2d8ad06c98","tid":1865163,"uid":202904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89273e8f016bf20ef45f0c55565ab4d047d6812a","tid":1865163,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb8a2958dc343b90afaf2af5f91b7ed3ad271143","tid":1865163,"uid":126376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c9733f0cc818fe357dd62202de7353c3d5a09c6","tid":1865163,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258db27fbcc882b702024ff93c98df5824d457af","tid":1865163,"uid":197010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:44:11.000Z","msg":"撐"},{"pid":"de966c849467c059a852661bfca5b203bda9